&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conclusions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I. All desks are plates.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;II. All plates are desks.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;III. Some plates are trays.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;IV. All trays are desks.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Select the option that is related to the third word in the same way as the second word is related to the first word.&lt;/p&gt;

